{"id":33394,"date":"2019-10-22T16:46:00","date_gmt":"2019-10-22T11:16:00","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/?p=33394"},"modified":"2023-01-30T09:55:40","modified_gmt":"2023-01-30T04:25:40","slug":"mery-xisca-perello","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/mery-xisca-perello\/","title":{"rendered":"Mery &#8216;Xisca&#8217; Perello (Rafael Nadal&#8217;s Wife) Age, Husband, Family, Biography &amp; More"},"content":{"rendered":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/Xisca-Perello.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-33395\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/Xisca-Perello.jpg\" alt=\"Xisca Perello\" width=\"650\" height=\"434\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/Xisca-Perello.jpg 800w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/Xisca-Perello-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/Xisca-Perello-768x513.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p>Mery &#8216;Xisca&#8217; Perello is the wife of the famous tennis star Rafael Nadal. She works as a Project Director in Nadal&#8217;s charity, The Rafa Nadal Foundation.<\/p>\n<div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_62 counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-custom ez-toc-container-direction\">\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title\">Contents<\/p>\n<label for=\"ez-toc-cssicon-toggle-item-65bce1d3eda52\" class=\"ez-toc-cssicon-toggle-label\"><span class=\"\"><span class=\"eztoc-hide\" style=\"display:none;\">Toggle<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-icon-toggle-span\"><svg style=\"fill: #000000;color:#000000\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" class=\"list-377408\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M6 6H4v2h2V6zm14 0H8v2h12V6zM4 11h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2zM4 16h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2z\" fill=\"currentColor\"><\/path><\/svg><svg style=\"fill: #000000;color:#000000\" class=\"arrow-unsorted-368013\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" version=\"1.2\" baseProfile=\"tiny\"><path d=\"M18.2 9.3l-6.2-6.3-6.2 6.3c-.2.2-.3.4-.3.7s.1.5.3.7c.2.2.4.3.7.3h11c.3 0 .5-.1.7-.3.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7zM5.8 14.7l6.2 6.3 6.2-6.3c.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7c-.2-.2-.4-.3-.7-.3h-11c-.3 0-.5.1-.7.3-.2.2-.3.5-.3.7s.1.5.3.7z\"\/><\/svg><\/span><\/span><\/label><input type=\"checkbox\"  id=\"ez-toc-cssicon-toggle-item-65bce1d3eda52\"  aria-label=\"Toggle\" \/><nav><ul class='ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1 ' ><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/mery-xisca-perello\/#WikiBiography\" title=\"Wiki\/Biography\">Wiki\/Biography<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/mery-xisca-perello\/#Physical_Appearance\" title=\"Physical Appearance\">Physical Appearance<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/mery-xisca-perello\/#Family_Husband\" title=\"Family &amp; Husband\">Family &amp; Husband<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/mery-xisca-perello\/#Career\" title=\"Career\">Career<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/mery-xisca-perello\/#FactsTrivia\" title=\"Facts\/Trivia\">Facts\/Trivia<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"WikiBiography\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #800080;\">Wiki\/Biography<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Maria Francisca Perello was born on Thursday, 7 July 1988 (<strong>age 31 years; as in 2019<\/strong>) in Palma, Spain. Her zodiac sign is Cancer. Her real name is Mery, but she prefers to be called by her nickname &#8220;Xisca&#8221;. She did her schooling from a local school in Spain. She was in the same school as Rafael Nadal, but they were in different classes. She obtained her Business Administration Degree from London, UK.<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/xisca-perello-.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-33407\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/xisca-perello-.jpg\" alt=\"Xisca Perello\" width=\"400\" height=\"225\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/xisca-perello-.jpg 600w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/xisca-perello--300x169.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Physical_Appearance\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #800080;\">Physical Appearance<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><strong>Height (approx.):<\/strong> 5&#8242; 9&#8243;<\/p>\n<p><strong>Eye Colour:<\/strong> Dark Brown<\/p>\n<p><strong>Hair Colour:<\/strong> Dark Brown<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/Xisca-Perello1.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-33405\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/Xisca-Perello1.jpg\" alt=\"Xisca Perello\" width=\"300\" height=\"633\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/Xisca-Perello1.jpg 379w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/Xisca-Perello1-142x300.jpg 142w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Family_Husband\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #800080;\">Family &amp; Husband<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Xisca is of Spanish ethnicity and she believes in Agnosticism. Her father&#8217;s name is Bernat Perell\u00f3 and her mother&#8217;s name is Mar\u00eda Pascual. She is in a long term relationship with ace tennis player Rafael Nadal. They started dating in 2005 after they met through a common friend. In May 2018, Nadal proposed to her, and they got engaged. On 19 October 2019, Xisca and Rafael Nadal got married to each other in Majorca, Spain.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_33400\" style=\"width: 410px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/Xisca-Perello-with-Rafael-Nadal-after-getting-married.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-33400\" class=\"wp-image-33400\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/Xisca-Perello-with-Rafael-Nadal-after-getting-married.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"267\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/Xisca-Perello-with-Rafael-Nadal-after-getting-married.jpg 800w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/Xisca-Perello-with-Rafael-Nadal-after-getting-married-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/Xisca-Perello-with-Rafael-Nadal-after-getting-married-768x512.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-33400\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Xisca Perello with Rafael Nadal after getting married<\/p><\/div>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Career\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #800080;\">Career<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>After Xisca finished her college studies, she got a job at a sporting firm named &#8220;MAPFRE&#8221;. MAPFRE was also a sponsor for Rafael Nadal at the time. However, Xisca had to quit from her job soon as many of her colleagues started a rumour that she had got her job only because of Nadal. Xisca then moved back to Spain, and she started working in an insurance company. In 2008, Nadal started his charity foundation named, The Rafa Nadal Foundation. Xisca joined his foundation as a Projects Director, a post which she still holds on to.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_33410\" style=\"width: 410px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/Xisca-Perello-with-Rafael-Nadal-at-the-Rafa-Nadal-Foundation-Office.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-33410\" class=\"wp-image-33410\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/Xisca-Perello-with-Rafael-Nadal-at-the-Rafa-Nadal-Foundation-Office.jpg\" alt=\"Xisca Perello with Rafael Nadal at the Rafa Nadal Foundation Office\" width=\"400\" height=\"290\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/Xisca-Perello-with-Rafael-Nadal-at-the-Rafa-Nadal-Foundation-Office.jpg 800w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/Xisca-Perello-with-Rafael-Nadal-at-the-Rafa-Nadal-Foundation-Office-300x217.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/Xisca-Perello-with-Rafael-Nadal-at-the-Rafa-Nadal-Foundation-Office-768x556.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-33410\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Xisca Perello with Rafael Nadal at the Rafa Nadal Foundation Office<\/p><\/div>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"FactsTrivia\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #800080;\">Facts\/Trivia<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Xisca is a reserved person and she does not like media attention. She has always stayed away from the media. Once in an interview, when asked why did she stay away from the media, she responded-<br \/>\n<blockquote><p>It\u2019s not a world I want to be part of, nor do I think Rafa would have chosen to be with a woman who looked for that in life.\u201d<\/p><\/blockquote>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>She rarely attends Nadal&#8217;s matches. Although she had appeared in a few matches of Nadal in the tournaments like Wimbledon and French Open, she had never appeared in any such match of the Australian Open until 2017, when she appeared in a match of the Australian Open where Nadal had been participating for the last 10 years, in an interview, she said-<br \/>\n<blockquote><p>We mutually decided to give each other space. Nadal needs space while competing and I would get tired if I had to just hang around waiting on his needs. If I followed him everywhere, I think there\u2019s a risk we might stop getting along\u201d<\/p><\/blockquote>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>After she quit her job in London, news of her relationship with Nadal surfaced, and she had to face a lot of media attention. People would photograph her everywhere she goes. Whenever she used to accompany Nadal, the paparazzi would come and take pictures of them together and also request an interview with Xisca.\n<p><div id=\"attachment_33413\" style=\"width: 410px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/Xisca-Perello-with-Rafael-Nadal3.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-33413\" class=\"wp-image-33413\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/Xisca-Perello-with-Rafael-Nadal3.jpg\" alt=\"Xisca Perello with Rafael Nadal\" width=\"400\" height=\"401\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/Xisca-Perello-with-Rafael-Nadal3.jpg 540w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/Xisca-Perello-with-Rafael-Nadal3-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/Xisca-Perello-with-Rafael-Nadal3-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/Xisca-Perello-with-Rafael-Nadal3-65x65.jpg 65w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-33413\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Xisca Perello with Rafael Nadal<\/p><\/div><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>Once, she was asked that why didn&#8217;t she quit her job and tour with Nadal, she responded-<br \/>\n<blockquote><p>It would asphyxiate me and then he would have to be worrying about me.\u201d<\/p><\/blockquote>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>In July 2018, she was first spotted wearing her engagement ring. She was attending Nadal&#8217;s match at Wimbledon when she was seen wearing the ring, after their engagement in May 2018.\n<p><div id=\"attachment_33416\" style=\"width: 410px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/Xisca-Perello-spotted-wearing-her-engagement-ring.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-33416\" class=\"wp-image-33416\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/Xisca-Perello-spotted-wearing-her-engagement-ring.jpg\" alt=\"Xisca Perello spotted wearing her engagement ring\" width=\"400\" height=\"344\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/Xisca-Perello-spotted-wearing-her-engagement-ring.jpg 547w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/Xisca-Perello-spotted-wearing-her-engagement-ring-300x258.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-33416\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Xisca Perello spotted wearing her engagement ring<\/p><\/div><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<div class=\"489bcfb86580b123547338c91db0eff2\" data-index=\"3\" style=\"float: none; margin:3px 0 3px 0; text-align:center;\">\n<ins class=\"adsbygoogle\"\r\n     style=\"display:block\"\r\n     data-ad-format=\"autorelaxed\"\r\n     data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-6769524711517462\"\r\n     data-ad-slot=\"2473600074\"><\/ins>\n<\/div>\n\n<div style=\"font-size: 0px; height: 0px; line-height: 0px; margin: 0; padding: 0; clear: both;\"><\/div>","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Mery &#8216;Xisca&#8217; Perello is the wife of the famous tennis star Rafael Nadal. She works as a Project Director in Nadal&#8217;s charity, The Rafa Nadal Foundation. Wiki\/Biography Maria Francisca Perello was born on Thursday, 7 July 1988 (age 31 years; as in 2019) in Palma, Spain. Her zodiac sign is Cancer. Her real name is Mery, but she prefers to be called by her nickname &#8220;Xisca&#8221;. She did her schooling from a local school in Spain. She was in the same school as Rafael Nadal, but they were in different classes. She obtained her Business Administration Degree from London, UK. <\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":33,"featured_media":33395,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[2,11],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/33394"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/33"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=33394"}],"version-history":[{"count":6,"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/33394\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":142892,"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/33394\/revisions\/142892"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/33395"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=33394"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=33394"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=33394"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}